# Nokta Academy Management System - Complete Project Documentation

## 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW

### Project Name
Nokta Academy Management System

### Technology Stack
- **Full-Stack JavaScript/TypeScript Application**
- Modern, scalable architecture with high-performance frontend and clean backend
- Production-ready with PWA offline support

### Frontend Technologies
- **React 18** - Latest React with concurrent features and hooks
- **Vite** - Fast build tool and development server
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first CSS framework for responsive design
- **React Query (TanStack Query)** - Powerful data fetching and caching library
- **Zustand** - Lightweight state management for global auth state
- **React Router DOM** - Client-side routing with protected routes
- **i18next** - Internationalization support (English/Persian)
- **Framer Motion** - Animation library for smooth transitions
- **Lucide Icons** - Modern icon library
- **Vite PWA Plugin** - Progressive Web App support

### Backend Technologies
- **Node.js** - JavaScript runtime for server-side development
- **Express.js** - Fast, unopinionated web framework
- **MongoDB** - NoSQL document database
- **Mongoose** - MongoDB object modeling for Node.js
- **TypeScript** - Typed JavaScript for better code quality
- **JWT (JSON Web Tokens)** - Secure authentication tokens
- **bcryptjs** - Password hashing library
- **Joi** - Schema validation library

### Database
- **MongoDB** - Document-based NoSQL database
- **Mongoose ODM** - Object Data Modeling for MongoDB
- **Auto-generated ObjectIds** - No manual ID management required
- **Optimized queries** with proper indexing
- **Relationships** via ObjectId references

### Authentication
- **JWT Authentication** with access and refresh tokens
- **Secure password hashing** using bcryptjs
- **Token refresh mechanism** for seamless user experience
- **Session management** with automatic logout on token expiry

### Authorization
- **Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)** with 7 distinct roles:
  - `super_admin` - Full system access
  - `admin` - Administrative access
  - `teacher` - Teaching and student management
  - `student` - Personal data access
  - `family_student` - Family member access to student data
  - `accountant` - Finance and expense management
  - `librarian` - Library and book management
- **Protected routes** with role-based permissions
- **API-level authorization** middleware

### State Management
- **Zustand** - Global authentication state management
- **React Query** - Server state management with caching
- **Local storage** - Persistent auth tokens
- **Optimistic updates** for better UX

### Offline Support / PWA
- **Service Worker** - Background caching and offline functionality
- **Web App Manifest** - Installable PWA with app-like experience
- **Offline navigation** - Cached routes work without internet
- **Auto-update** - Service worker updates automatically
- **Cache-first strategy** - Fast loading from cache when available
- **Local profile asset support** - backend seed script generates local profile images for teachers and students
- **Uploads runtime caching** - service worker caches `/uploads/*` image assets for offline profile display

### Performance Optimization
- **Lazy loading** - Route-based and component-based code splitting
- **Memoization** - React.memo for expensive components
- **Bundle optimization** - Tree shaking and minification
- **Generic CRUD engine** - Single component handles all data operations
- **File count reduction** - From 100+ files to ~30 files
- **API caching** - React Query intelligent caching
- **Image optimization** - Efficient asset loading
- **Debounced search** - Optimized search performance

